{
  "text": "\u2022 C. Upon 3 days of in vitro culture maintenance, SCs were incubated with 10 mM tris(hydroxymethyl)aminometane hydrochloride buffer (TRIS) (Sigma Chemical Co), as previously reported in the literature, in order to eliminate the residual germinal cells [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
